						               													<description>Boozle is a party game perfect for up to eight players. Boozles are party animals. They come in many colors and each have their own style of drinking. To win the game all you have to do is collect five Boozles of the same color by drawing them and stealing them from other players. Outmaneuver your friends and force them to drink while you steal their precious Boozles!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Each player has the same five actions available to them: Snatch, Nope, Drink, Draw and Repeat.  At the beginning of each turn all players simultaneously choose two of their actions and play them in secret.  Players then go around the table revealing and resolving their actions until everyone has used both of their actions.  At this point the actions go back into your hand and the turn starts over.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;    Poozles (purple) are classy fellows. They drink like sirs.&amp;#10;    Roozles (red) are angry drunks. If something wasn't destroyed, the night wasn't a success. &amp;#10;    Yoozles (yellow) are the life of the party. Free rounds and high-fives for everyone.&amp;#10;    Groozles (green) are a bit much. They always take things one step too far. &amp;#10;    Bloozles (blue) are drama queens. If they aren't making a scene, they're crying in the corner.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
